{"tid":1352562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律師有野講 2 - 請和理非入","createTime":"2019-07-22T20:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T15:03:31.000Z","uid":43204,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"755ab29c03b53b5825af0557ddc7304a65cffea8","tid":1352562,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:24:16.000Z","msg":"(代POST)<br />\n<br />\n律師有野講 2 - 請和理非入<br />\n<br />\n原POST - <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1323465/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1323465/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n文中所寫請大家再細讀及善用&ldquo;追故&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nSorry 消費左律師二字, 今次不講法律, 只講香城ONLINE - Black Bloc更新版, <br />\n<br />\n<ins><div style=\"text-align: center;\">TLDR  Summary </div></ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">A 請所有遊行/集會人士 (不論男女老幼) <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黑TEE包頭</span></strong><br />\n當群眾一半以上<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Black Bloc</span></strong> 保證不出3次定會變天<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/tLde1zA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtLde1zA.png&h=559f0ca2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nB 放棄道德枷鎖<br />\nC 定deadline -&gt; 升級<br />\nD 已揭竿起義, 以後請以Patriot of Hong Kong 稱呼<br />\nE 習武<br />\nF冷處理自殺者</span><br />\nG 除血水外, 自己裝備自己帶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><ins>I) 至和理非</ins></div></ins><br />\n<br />\n1.內爭進行中, 你我手中染血, 所有香港人請歸邊 <br />\n2.想成功就須要進化, 改變思維係第一步 (大BOSS是無底線的)<br />\nA<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請「放棄道德枷鎖」</span></span></strong>, 2019既遊行係為保護勇武而行, 行完請留守<br />\nB Black Bloc 要多人做先有效<br />\n請所有遊行人士 (不論男女老幼) 都著純黑TEE及黑TEE包頭<br />\n所有和理非都black bloc先保護到其他人<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">包頭唔係因為要做犯法野</span></strong>, 而係要等怪唔知你會做乜野 <br />\n當群眾一半以上Black Bloc, 保證不出3次必定變天<br />\n(Black Bloc 出街是絕對合法的, 有穆斯林保護)<br />\nC <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">放棄 等人救心態</span></strong> (包括但不限於: 外國, 聯合國, 天朝, 正苦) 自己香港自己救!</span><br />\nD 唔好再叫 &ldquo;冷靜&rdquo;/阻止他人行事, 人善被人欺<br />\n<br />\n3.習武, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「以武制暴」</span></strong>, 喪屍隨時會出現係身邊,唔會因為你舉高雙手而唔咬你 (e.g.元朗戰役), 好好保護家人<br />\n<br />\n4.咁多年來係各位參與遊行人士都只係有一種  <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">追求 :公義 (Justice)</span></strong></span> <br />\n公義唔等於法律, 只係好多人會透過法律去尋求公義 (包括法律界及法瞎)<br />\nNatural Justice (自然公義?) 依件個個都以為有既寶石, 其實從來都唔係香城Online 隻GAME入面<br />\n<br />\n詳見如下 <br />\n(純粹個人理解）根據基本法，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人大係有&ldquo;redefining law&quot; （即文內的&ldquo;interpretation&quot;) 既絕對權</span></strong> (plenary powers), 香港法庭無權唔跟/挑戰 （HK court has no jurisdiction over NPCSC interpretation/decision) <br />\n<br />\n法庭1999年已經確認, 這是飯民律師們唔會告訴大眾的 <br />\n<br />\n講白d 就係基本法依隻game, 人大係programmer 可以隨時改code 而香城人係無得唔玩 未來30年仲會加難度<br />\n<br />\n5. 退場時請幫手有物資 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><div style=\"text-align: center;\">II) 至近戰玩家</div></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1.黑社會係限時special event, 比大家刷經驗升級的<br />\n(發現後只得幾分鐘打) </span></span></strong><br />\n打之前請確保武器夠長夠硬 (至少60cm長) <br />\n隻怪D棍應該100-120CM, 刀50cm+<br />\n2.刀則一吋短一吋險<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vjJ3KxgKgE8&amp;list=PL43zKVCi9RLmo0T6_cSrVmQl8S9rg2pCA&amp;index=4&amp;t=0s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvjJ3KxgKgE8%26list%3DPL43zKVCi9RLmo0T6_cSrVmQl8S9rg2pCA%26index%3D4%26t%3D0s&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjSrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=bf8faf89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vjJ3KxgKgE8&amp;list=PL43zKVCi9RLmo0T6_cSrVmQl8S9rg2pCA&amp;index=4&amp;t=0s</a><br />\n3.只帶口罩係會吸引喪屍伏擊的, 請入TOWN 換黑TEE<br />\n4.一方陣亡只係時間問題, 請以唔係你死就我亡心態應戰<br />\n5.支援人數少時請勿戀戰<br />\n6.必要時, 學習 「暗殺」 , cookbook 技能- <br />\n7. 下午為開戰佳時, 22:00左右如果仲拉鋸緊請考慮擇日再戰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><div style=\"text-align: center;\">III) 至文宜</div></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n1.國際層面上要出師有名, 請統一以terrorist attack /lawless night 形容元朗, 另加Government backed thugs <br />\n2.請以Patriot of Hong Kong <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">去信G20 progress update</span></span></strong>, 要求各國及聯合國盡快介入, 以免人命傷亡, (928為最後最後死線)  <br />\n3.6名被disconnect 的議員已經係臨時議會, 臨時政府就攻佔陣地後再宣佈<br />\n4.(red alert 更新版) 國際關係及黑社會只講利益, 請考量以香城失手後世界會染紅, 紅色入侵(red termite) 作切入 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">IV) 就自殺者/ 想自殺者</div></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n請不要矯情,美化, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冷處理</span></strong>就好<br />\n臨陣脫逃係不負責任既表現<br />\n戰士應該係戰死沙場<br />\n尋死者, 請以神風死士方式明志, 才值得大定尊重<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPatriot of Hong Kong<br />\n2019年7月23日"},{"pid":"64b9d4993ea7d19b30016a19b98ed01c8a41a678","tid":1352562,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:25:18.000Z","msg":"開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2b42838f63f8bf98f71a5a8a7092efa8d0f8d9","tid":1352562,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:34:10.000Z","msg":"(唔係講合唔合理)<br />\n講漏左, 驚署差唔多每次遊行完拉人後都落閘的<br />\n有無人包圍都落"},{"pid":"3cec1974519f3714c10f2d65220a44bace1e1979","tid":1352562,"uid":263973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:39:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"79f862fd386233ddd15e32163d3d508d380d12d0","tid":1352562,"uid":191765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:41:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4a505532439929d4eb6b3bf4a71db3179d84ad75","tid":1352562,"uid":145758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T21:22:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f9d379de16e70d5682d6bb5e82ec71473ad3013","tid":1352562,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:47:49.000Z","msg":"(代POST)<br />\n<ins><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>III) 至文宜</strong></div></ins><br />\n(後加)<br />\n5. 加強向遊客宣傳, 比如<br />\na) 城人係 fight for democracy and freedom, 抗赤<br />\nb) 必要時, 提出旅遊警示 (7傷拳黎, 因為少左外國人就少左一個向外傳播既渠道,變相少一份保障<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>6. BLACK BLOC BLACK BLOC BLACK BLOC</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3dc1be266ee8b64ba9d8a3f6d588c851589d5b8b","tid":1352562,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果無用就由佢沉"},{"pid":"43fcffe806ce1d8a5ba5a0288d94dd13fa807e52","tid":1352562,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:36:47.000Z","msg":"律師們<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.doj.gov.hk/eng/public/pdf/pd2011/Feature_Articles.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.doj.gov.hk%2Feng%2Fpublic%2Fpdf%2Fpd2011%2FFeature_Articles.pdf&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjSrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=feafb6e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.doj.gov.hk/eng/public/pdf/pd2011/Feature_Articles.pdf</a><br />\n（p3)<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/R_v_Dytham\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FR_v_Dytham&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjSrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=a18b2668\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/R_v_Dytham</a><br />\n<br />\n請考慮建議受傷人士 告MTR, 警方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而未見律師們既 千奇唔好簽任何法律文件"},{"pid":"506163df0c29d9e23d75d7519a38931e7e1db871","tid":1352562,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SbRpUXe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSbRpUXe.jpg&h=40a5a356&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80a53581df81cc0e352c631e3194e8f0ae00a90d","tid":1352562,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20bf4db4fc40ab3